// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1373 — Mass File Rename (suncrypt)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: cd059a3a-91df-59c1-9243-328718863873

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
